## Quantitative Synthesis — Preconditions {{ "x" | calc }}

Every statistical method is gated behind its preconditions. A pooled estimate is emitted only when ≥2 studies report the same canonical outcome on a commensurable metric **and** share a compatible case definition; small-study-effect tests (Egger / funnel) require ≥10 studies.

